So the basic functionality I am looking for is "templated screens". I want to have a base screen, that can be included into other screens, but when the base screen is updated, it gets updated everywhere. For example, I would be able to have a "Create", "Edit", "View" screen for an issue type (each locked down by permissions), but each of those screens have the same "Asset Location" Screen as a tab within them. So instead of a "Create_Asset_Location", "Edit_Asset_Location", and "View_Asset_Location" screen (each of which needs updated if new location metadata is added), I want a "Asset_Location" screen that gets tied to each "Create", "Edit", "View" Screen as a tab. Only update the "Asset_Location" screen, and it works on the other three.

